4Geeks Academy offers a "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer" course. This course is designed for individuals with no previous knowledge who want to start a career as a data scientist and build their first machine learning models. The course lasts for 16 weeks, with 3 classes per week and a maximum of 12 students per class. The course covers topics such as Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics. Students will learn to create predictive models using Python and libraries such as Pandas and Numpy, and explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. They will also work with supervised and unsupervised learning models. The course includes practical assignments and real-life case studies to prepare students for the challenges they will face in their careers. Students will also have the opportunity to strategize and develop their own AI projects, following the complete lifecycle from development to deployment and maintenance. The course is available in both English and Spanish, with live classes taught in the language of the campus. Upon completion of the course, students will receive a recognized certificate. For more information, visit the website: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop